<p><tags><tag kind="heading2">## </tag></tags>Ulysses for iPhone and iPad</p>
<p></p>
<p>If you own Ulysses for iPhone and iPad (and, frankly, <element kind="link"><attribute identifier="URL">http://ulyssesapp.com/ios</attribute><attribute identifier="title">Ulysses for iPhone and iPad</attribute>you should</element>), now is a good time to enable iCloud on your devices. You will be able to edit all your texts on your iPhone and/or iPad. There’s no further setup necessary, no linking, nothing.</p>
<p></p>
<p>Start writing at home and continue on the road. Or the coffee shop. Or the beach. The bed. The couch. The Eiffel Tower. Mount Everest. ISS. Kepler 21b. So cool.</p>
